"sponsor FreeBSD events, and provide travel grants to FreeBSD developers. You "
"are also helping us represent the Project in executing contracts, license "
"agreements, copyrights, trademarks, and other legal arrangements that "
"require a recognized legal entity."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
